{"tid":260193,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)奪寶奇兵1-4","createTime":"2017-05-27T13:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T20:58:04.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7285d0d207c4527a996d4dc5021d6f64f5fcb974","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=dOZkJEEeTMgEOzb72xmK%2FGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ce140131\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=dOZkJEEeTMgEOzb72xmK%2FGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b931ad5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=dOZkJEEeTMgEOzb72xmK%2FGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d40ab6c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4b/Raiders.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4b%2FRaiders.jpg&h=c4e52631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1936年，寶物獵人及考古學家印第安納&middot;瓊斯勇闖秘魯叢林，在充滿危險機關的古廟中尋找黃金神像。逃出古廟後，他卻遇見競爭對手：另一個考古學家瑞尼貝拉克以及他率領的土人，被迫交出他找到的金像。突破重圍後，印第安納&middot;瓊斯登上一艘早就安排好的水上飛機逃離了叢林。<br />\n<br />\n短暫停留美國後，他回到校園教授考古學。兩個陸軍情報人員到他的學校告訴他，德國納粹黨正在追求未知的神秘武力，並在追捕他的老師艾伯納瑞文伍德。瑞文伍德擁有稱為「拉雅之桿」頂端的元件<br />\n<br />\n2.1935年，考古學教授印第安納&middot;瓊斯帶著夜總會歌女威莉和12歲的孤兒小滑溜在中國上海一起逃命冒險，逃脫後意外到了一個破落的印度小村莊，這個小村落的所有幼童和村裡的3塊珍貴聖石都失蹤了。印第安納&middot;瓊斯承諾協助村長尋回失蹤的3塊珍貴聖石和兒童外，來到了盤踞邪惡勢力控制的王室宮殿，找出3塊具有神秘法力的寶石。印第安納&middot;瓊斯他們再度展開驚險的鬥智鬥力和奪寶追逐戰<br />\n<br />\n3.考古學教授印第安納&middot;瓊斯的父親亨利&middot;瓊斯教授，因為研究並尋找傳說中的耶穌聖杯而失蹤。由於德國納粹黨也要奪取有神奇力量的聖杯，印第安納&middot;瓊斯和父親必須在奧地利及德國納粹黨軍隊追殺下冒險死裡逃生。<br />\n<br />\n4.本片時代背景設置於《聖戰奇兵》的19年後，也就是1957年，而印第安納&middot;瓊斯博士則過著很平靜的生活，但是他隨後必須要對抗蘇聯幹員，爭奪水晶骷髏。故事設定水晶骷髏有可能是外星人或是古代馬雅文明所遺留。印第安納&middot;瓊斯博士的冒險則橫跨新墨西哥州、康乃狄克州、墨西哥市以及秘魯叢林。<br />\n<br />\n10 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fd4469cf885ff6beb197768e28e86b8173eacf","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5fbfe19407b4c744780da2cc900d0a782324c8","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1814142f68a0f7a4ed5d066b14473491f14bd7e","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78428ca53236bab3e82ce453e2a10be3f72ebb05","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684e1a56f2c9d3cda34a3d8936ba17b6a23c7ccb","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc3ead8b58d35a1aeac5ca5318e7eab9ce70a01","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db6c653e81c98bdb8356dedccf641006e3ee287","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47d1af27033d26f92313681ebb5f378eb76c06f","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06aa4ea9f99583c0859abcea712c6cced6f90722","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290fe6dfa537c314ae9d9e5ad9d8baba085e3ba1","tid":260193,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}